	<div class="services">
		<div class="services-section">
			<h2>Digital Marketing</h2>
			<p>Marketing across the paid, owned and earned landscape, online and offline, is no easy feat. Consider us your special ops digital team, focused on marrying your marketing efforts with focused digital marketing and media strategies. Our goal? Ensuring you have a tailored, integrated presence, where and when you should be, with impactful messaging and creative built to live across platforms.</p>
		</div>
 		<div class="services-section">
			<h2>Communications</h2>
			<p>Gone are the days of vertical media outlets and controlled consumer entry points to branded content. As traditional PR, media, and marketing continue to morph into the melting pot brands are now tasked with navigating, one indispensable purpose remains: the ability to establish meaningful engagement through storytelling. Whether developing a comprehensive social marketing campaign or informing a high-level PR strategy, we’re well-accustomed to working with agency partners and across internal teams to integrate communications efforts and ensure for consistent messaging across all media touch points.</p>
		</div>
	 	<div class="services-section">
			<h2>Content Creation: Design + Build</h2>
			<p>Positioned at the intersection of entertainment, advertising, and technology and working with our parent company <a target="_blank" href="http://www.click3x.com">Click <span style="font-family:serif;">3</span>X</a>, our expert team of designers, directors, animators, producers and technologists create innovative, solutions-driven digital experiences that shape the media landscape.</p>
			<p>Our video expertise covers the full content ecosystem, from concept, to in-house design, animation, production and editing though to content marketing and distribution, making content development seamless from start to finish.</p>
			<p>Our robust, cost-effective digital execution capabilities include websites, display ads, social media content, mobile apps and out-of-home interactive experiences.</p>
